OL,3,CParents raise awareness of epilepsy
OL,4,Ccomplications after daughter's death
OL,6,FAmber's parents, Martin and Amanda
OL,7,FWalker, want more people to be aware
OL,8,Fof the risk of SUDEP and say more open
OL,9,Fdiscussions are needed.
OL,11,FMartin Walker, Amber's father, said:
OL,12,F"I think she managed amazingly. You
OL,13,Funderestimate how difficult it must
OL,14,Fhave been for her and I think she did
OL,15,Fstruggle but she did incredibly well.
OL,17,F"She worked, she had good humour, she
OL,18,Fmade us laugh a lot, she drove us nuts
OL,19,Fas well, but she coped with it pretty
OL,20,Fwell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
