OL,3,CParents raise awareness of epilepsy
OL,4,Ccomplications after daughter's death
OL,6,F"I think the one thing we weren't ever
OL,7,Fprepared for, was the fact that
OL,8,Fsomeone could suddenly die."
OL,10,FAmanda Walker, Amber's mother, said:
OL,11,F"We never even heard of it, we'd been
OL,12,Fin the system since she was 12 years
OL,13,Fold to when she died at 22.
OL,15,F"Not one clinician had ever mentioned
OL,16,FSUDEP. She died while we were away in
OL,17,FAustralia which was really harsh for
OL,18,Fus.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
