OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F415A1728635132
OL,3,CParents raise awareness of epilepsy
OL,4,Ccomplications after daughter's death
OL,6,F"I mean it's harsh anyway but it's an
OL,7,Fother worldly pain to have that happen
OL,8,Fto you."
OL,10,FIt was the first time Amber's parents
OL,11,Fhad left her with her brother and
OL,12,Fsister, who were educated about how to
OL,13,Fdeal with a seizure.
OL,15,FSammy Ashby, CEO, SUDEP Action, said:
OL,16,F"Because we know that many epilepsy
OL,17,Fdeaths are preventable, there's a lot
OL,18,Fof steps that we can take to try and
OL,19,Fhelp people live as safely as possible
OL,20,Fwith their epilepsy and that's what we
OL,21,Freally want to try and get across.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
