PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F415A1728635132
OL,3,CParents raise awareness of epilepsy
OL,4,Ccomplications after daughter's death
OL,6,F"So things like getting as best
OL,7,Fseizure control as you can, taking
OL,8,Fyour medication regularly and
OL,9,Freliably, making sure you're on the
OL,10,Fbest medication for you, they're all
OL,11,Fthings that can really help but also
OL,12,Fjust knowing about the risks."
OL,14,FMartin and Amber Walker believe more
OL,15,Fawareness of the condition is needed
OL,16,Fto prevent other families suffering
OL,17,Fthe same loss that they have.
OL,19,FAmanda said: "You think that it's
OL,20,Fnever going to happen to you and then
OL,21,Fit's why, why did it happen to us?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
