OL,6,F"Then you think well actually it's not
OL,7,Fjust us, why not us? But the pain is
OL,8,Fjust indescribable, it's other
OL,9,Fworldly."
OL,11,FMartin said: "It just leaves a massive
OL,12,Fhole, it's a shock. Sudden death is a
OL,13,Fshock, but in a youngster with so much
OL,14,Flife to live and so much talent, so
OL,15,Fmuch to give the world."
